accessibility.text: Here is a juicy real world question, use these resources to find an answer. You/Your group will present it to the class (Socratic Electronics)

Jigsaw Exercises: Student groups based around a component or item in an equation, then the groups reshuffle so there is one “domain expert” per new project group for the next step which might be solving a word problem or making something.
